    __webpack_exports__["default"] = "<h1 class='mat-display-1'>👨‍💻 My Work</h1>\n\n<div class='wrapper' [ngStyle]=\"{'max-height': hidden ? closedHeight + 'px' : '2000px', 'transition': 'max-height 300ms'}\">\n  <div #firstElement style=\"margin-bottom: 100px;\">\n    <small class='primary'>FEB 2019 - PRESENT</small>\n    <h2>United States Cold Storage ❄️️</h2>\n    <h3 class='mat-subheading-1'>Junior Java Developer</h3>\n    <mat-chip-list>\n      <mat-chip>Angular</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>Spring</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>Java</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>SQL</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>DB2</mat-chip>\n    </mat-chip-list>\n    <p>\n      Developing and maintaining code for the company's electronic warehouse management system based on Java EE and the\n      Spring framework.<br>\n      Maintaining and enhancing the application's web interface based on Java Server Pages served with Spring MVC and\n      single page Angular applications.<br>\n      Creating a Python script that allows easy, platform independent setup of the development environment.<br>\n      Developing a proof of concept to containerize several applications using Docker in order to enable a continuous\n      development environment and possible deployment to the cloud.<br>\n      State of the art single page application frontend development with Angular leveraging RxJS and the NgRx state\n      management library.<br>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"margin-bottom: 100px;\">\n    <small class='primary'>FEB 2019 - PRESENT</small>\n    <h2>United States Cold Storage ❄️️</h2>\n    <h3 class='mat-subheading-1'>Junior Java Developer</h3>\n    <mat-chip-list>\n      <mat-chip>Angular</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>Spring</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>Java</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>SQL</mat-chip>\n      <mat-chip>DB2</mat-chip>\n    </mat-chip-list>\n    <p>\n      Developing and maintaining code for the company's electronic warehouse management system based on Java EE and the\n      Spring framework.<br>\n      Maintaining and enhancing the application's web interface based on Java Server Pages served with Spring MVC and\n      single page Angular applications.<br>\n      Creating a Python script that allows easy, platform independent setup of the development environment.<br>\n      Developing a proof of concept to containerize several applications using Docker in order to enable a continuous\n      development environment and possible deployment to the cloud.<br>\n      State of the art single page application frontend development with Angular leveraging RxJS and the NgRx state\n      management library.<br>\n    </p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<button mat-button (click)='toggleWork()'>{{ hidden ? \"See More\" : \"Hide\"}}</button>\n";
